Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公，暑假我们一起去海边玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.49,0:00:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁要跟你一起去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.89,0:00:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然老公这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.82,0:00:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是前几天作梦有梦到我对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦到你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.33,0:00:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作梦还会梦到我\N表示我们的关系已经很不错了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次被梦到了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过是做梦想要我怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.84,0:00:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次穿着泳衣被丢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.35,0:00:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了也还是\N好喜欢好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一副臭脸\N也依然是那么迷人
