Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一．起．来．吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那天以来的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.97,0:01:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论何时都希望能感觉的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.25,0:01:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管到哪里都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.15,0:01:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管做什么都好让人心动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷入恋爱的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都好像魔法师一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以让人高兴起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.44,0:01:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了也还是\N好喜欢好喜欢
