Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.26,0:02:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.23,0:02:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情书大混乱!左右为难的恋爱!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，太天真了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泳衣的魅力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是像这样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个夏天，我会用我的魅力\N和岩城小弟谈一段美好的恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后成为白雪公主的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白雪公主?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在王子的亲吻之下获得了奇蹟的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白雪公主变成了美丽的王妃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.47,0:02:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就跟那个一样\N恋爱是从接吻之后才算正式开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而暑假正是追求爱情的大好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要带岩城小弟到海边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后让他拜倒在大人的魅力之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的胜算...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干爹C好厉害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌，我怎么会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我也要和老公到海边加油喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇!怎么了怎么了，这么突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵你也要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油...什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如说跟老公在海边...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.68,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有啊跟老公在民宿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.16,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有还有跟老公在海之家...\N(在海边提供饮食、租借等服务的店)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何?小葵想不想也像这样...咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到国三的夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会想到“跟喜欢的人接吻”吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假也许是最后的机会了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵你也有“老公”吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎、怎么可能有嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得不错的倒是有啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人叫什么名字啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶!不要啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我嘛，我会帮你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.36,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵之前帮了我这么多忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以这次换我来帮你写情书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，叫什么名字啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不可以说出去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.37,0:04:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是A班的凤凰院龙之介同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，说出来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A班的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人!他很有名耶，长的很帅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诚之介同学的话我是知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有这个人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之是龙之介同学对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊，原来如此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“你是照亮我心中的光芒”这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没办法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵，写好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.78,0:05:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...这个\N由、由我交给他吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.29,0:05:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.69,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，如果真的交给他之后\N进行的很顺利的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我还是不行啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这个也让我来吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向A班GO~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被拿去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凤凰院龙之介同学在吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦~我钟爱的少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，蔷薇之进同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙之介同学在吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道这是她最拿手的笑话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样的话如果我认真的回答她\N岂不是太不解风情了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想把这个交给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这、这这这这是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯!是情书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻烦你喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊，终于下定了决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.73,0:06:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是却又不好意思\N所以才用这么可爱的手段...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是多么动人又楚楚可怜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我钟爱的少女啊\N就趁这份感动尚未褪去之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看看你信里写了些什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.97,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办，怎么办，要是顺利的话...\N可以的，可以的，好期待好期待...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚凤凰院好像抓着什么信\N满脸通红的倒下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的!?成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来就等下个礼拜天\N两个人第一次约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后发生了很多事\N两人的感情越来越深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假的时候就，嗯~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌~那样太快了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还只是中学生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.34,0:06:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在图书馆看到的书上写说\N中学生到B的人有97%耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人!B是指什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯~A是“热情的吻”的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那B就是“非常热情的吻”!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌~太激烈了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么才大清早的\N心情就这么好啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为今天是小葵约会的日子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想说他们会进展到什么地步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次才没那么顺利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是B呢，还是C呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，C是什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是“超~级热情的吻”吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不提那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她知道你跟凤凰院之间的事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?啊，啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都这个时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.98,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公，要是小葵的约会\N进行得很顺利的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就亲一下当做奖励吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在说什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.19,0:07:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是努力的女孩子\N王子就会给她奇蹟的吻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔唷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少开玩笑了~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出门去了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，小葵好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一来就没问题了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙、龙之介同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，圣本同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那那那个，今、今、今天...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是巧呢，你也有约会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是要跟莉采儿小姐约会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶~怎么会怎么会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.16,0:08:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不是龙之介同学\N而是春团治同学来呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵，还是老样子那么爱说笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个人就是龙之介同学啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧，我钟爱的少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.94,0:08:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日就让我俩快乐地渡过这一天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我钟爱的少女?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是担心小葵才过来看看的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是健忘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是写了这封火辣辣的情书给我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...不是的\N这个是小葵要写给龙之介同学的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记写上名字了!\N耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那、那个...这个...所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个就这样...加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，拜拜~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心里只有你一个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃，那种事我从来没有考虑过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.71,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，你都已经来过我家了\N还称赞过我的收藏不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那段幸福的时光我是绝对不会忘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么怎么回事...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和龙之介同学做了那些事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...不是的...是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么没跟我说呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃，那个...该怎么说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.86,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好过份，我最讨厌莉采儿了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，等一下，小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵，等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙之介同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你终于记起来了，我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.11,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵她是真的真的\N很喜欢龙之介同学的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常总是很有精神\N甚至比男孩子还坚强的小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要一提到龙之介同学\N就变的心跳不止，脚也开始站不稳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那样的喜欢你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是这么的喜欢一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却没有获得任何的回报\N我想她可能非常的伤心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以请和小葵交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才那些话，我原封不动的还给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对你的感情，跟那是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，我已经有老公了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我也无法和圣本同学交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我到底该怎么办才好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.06,0:10:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想说如果能让大家都开心就好了...\N难道是我错了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干爹A、B、C!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有东西要找，请出动飞机吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能把被称为“梦幻小熊内裤”\N的“41's PRlNCESS”带来给我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,圣本同学的事我就再考虑看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不会说谎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会带回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“41's PRlNCESS”!?\N不...不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.09,0:11:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“41's PRlNCESS”可是\N足以堪称为梦幻的小熊内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去英国的登山家史顿布拉克\N曾在埃佛勒斯峰峰顶附近发现它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却又不小心弄丢了之后\N它的下落就再也没有人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然在他过世时留下的遗书中有声明\N只要是发现者即可拥有其所有权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.48,0:11:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在无数登山家的努力探寻之下\N至今依然没有人能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，小葵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是没能找到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，你醒了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，我还要去找东西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.73,0:11:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是我先麻烦莉采儿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却对你发这么大的脾气，是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我会拿出勇气来\N自己再努力看看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎样，你就再睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做的不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就为了帮朋友的忙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对你的评价得改一改了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就亲一下当作奖励吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇!你你、你起来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来嘛，奖励的亲亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么奖励的亲亲啊，白痴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家要奖励啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很烦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲亲，亲亲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太过份了!我才不会亲你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.56,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.81,0:13:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人和女人真是难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了查清楚我去了图书馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然对比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公是一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家好喜欢他，所以我不会哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.47,0:13:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不气馁，不逃避，更不会失去勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.61,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信总有一天春天会到来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.49,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿出认真的力量，认真的力量向前冲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.00,0:14:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶，又是我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啥?跟莉采儿相处一段时间后\N感觉如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙总是以她的方式在努力着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那点我是很称赞她啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.52,0:14:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是啊，这可不代表我承认\N跟那家伙结了婚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶，又是我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们还真闲啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啥?跟莉采儿相处一段时间后\N感觉如何?
